org.bluedb.api.keys

Interface BlueKey

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<BlueKey>, java.io.Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    HashGroupedKey, IndexCompositeKey, IntegerKey, LongKey, StringKey, TimeFrameKey, TimeKey, UUIDKey, ValueKey

    public interface BlueKey
extends java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<BlueKey>
    A key that can be mapped to a value in a BlueCollection or BlueIndex.

    Known implementations include TimeKey, TimeFrameKey, UUIDKey, StringKey, LongKey, IntegerKey
